properties.name: recurrence
properties.description: Recurrence. Can be set to `daily`, `weekly`, `monthly` or `yearly`

properties.name: recurrenceInterval
properties.description: Recurrence interval. Valid only when `recurrence` option is set.

properties.name: recurrenceEndDate
properties.description: Recurrence end date. Valid only when `recurrence` option is set.

properties.name: calendarName
properties.description: Calendar name. Ths is supported by `iOS` only.
